'''突破策略'''（{{Lang-en|Price channel}}）是常用於[[股票|股票]]或[[物價|物價]]，並轉換為[[統計圖表|線性趨勢圖表]]的[[市場行銷|市場行銷]]策略模式。<ref>{{Cite book |title=Technical Analysis of the Financial Markets |url=https://archive.org/details/technicalanalysi00murp_350 |last=Murphy |first=John J. |publisher=New York Institute of Finance |year=1999 |isbn=0735200661 |location=[[New_York|New York]] |pages=[https://archive.org/details/technicalanalysi00murp_350/page/n116 80]}}</ref>一對趨勢線有可能是水平、上升或下降的狀態。當價格的起伏範圍並非在代表支撐或阻力的趨勢線內時，那麼價格的趨勢即[[突破_(技術分析)|突破]]了正常的規律，因此買家需要透過交易策略進一步辨別是否為真突破，或是買家使用突破策略產生出的假突破現象。<ref>{{Cite book |title=Technical Analysis of the Financial Markets |url=https://archive.org/details/technicalanalysi00murp_350 |last=Murphy |first=John J. |publisher=New York Institute of Finance |year=1999 |isbn=0735200661 |location=[[New_York|New York]] |pages=[https://archive.org/details/technicalanalysi00murp_350/page/n446 400]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=外匯教學：『失敗的突破策略』 |url=https://www.incomore.com.tw/incomorecollege/learning-13237 |accessdate=2020-07-05 |publisher=INCOMORE交易學院 |language=zh}}</ref>

